Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说《人间失格》的作者太宰治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不擅长与人相处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这样一段逸闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太宰尊为师长的井伏鳟二 曾邀其来自家做客
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可左等右等都不见太宰上门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,井伏好生疑惑 出门一看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.61,0:00:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只见太宰在门外转来转去 就是想不出进门的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一段逸闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太宰曾邀请晚辈来家里交流感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想主动搭话 却不知说什么才好的太宰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.55,0:00:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等待晚辈时独自借酒浇愁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果竟喝得酩酊大醉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长与人相处的太宰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底害怕人身上的什么特质呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因名作 更显青涩 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:01:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看 人间失格第三话


Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（1932年）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 堀木先生做事太慢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等他做完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.92,0:01:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以发生在上海的日本僧侣遇害事件为契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.61,0:01:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各地频频发生中日冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府为保护留中日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定向上海派遣驱逐舰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸画得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就训了他一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 那是得训
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不去工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一直陪我在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算是活得像人样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一文不名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 我画的是真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会喜欢你真正的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这是真正的艺术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画这种不值钱的画 你能填饱肚子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一把年纪了连自己都养不活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有做人的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想自己赚钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老爸说过 赚不到钱的人就不是人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的画可比堀木画的好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的漫画的确画得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画？

Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那女人公敌画的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.69,0:05:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您别这么说他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也当心别着了他的道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这倒不赖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别公开他的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 虽然少了点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西居然能卖出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在编辑部也颇受好评呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人会喜欢那种画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实心里很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我能赚钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 要不去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会再画你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经是正常人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我好找
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 他是爸爸的熟人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又玩女人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:08:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长此以往 世间可不会放过你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间？世间是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 漫画卖了几个钱就口气就硬了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间就是世间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我有个认识的记者在打听你的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是想采访你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人公敌开始和女人同居了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次还带着个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.99,0:08:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了这消息他一定会开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你有钱了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的事我还没跟人说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂子讨厌那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我是生是死 都与这些人无关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是世间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真想你啊小帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这次的稿费
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你多了点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你不想赚更多钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会画画嘛 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想画画那事件的真相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事件是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 就三年前镰仓那事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间的人一定都很想看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎算了 抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再说 再说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（鲁邦酒馆）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛灌得这么凶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸长得这么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人放心不下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能是丑陋的妖怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想过普通人的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间却企图把我塑造成妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国政府宣布 失业人员已逾7百万
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失业者们为求一职 不断发起示威游行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.33,0:12:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府打算禁止这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.38,0:12:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真差劲


Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来包金蝙蝠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重的酒味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早的就喝酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人不舒服 真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.54,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 茂子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你是我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 胡子扎得好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饿了没 去吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂子才不是神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神在天上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对神许愿就什么都能实现 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茂子想要真正的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你杀了女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近的阿姨们说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…世间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀木 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你怎么彻夜不归啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一阵不见你又显老了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸好像病倒了 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“比目鱼”让我转交的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你津轻的大哥寄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你马上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得赶紧准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今我哪还有脸回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我成为让父亲大吃一惊的画家 否则就回不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会画三流漫画的男人还说什么大话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 偶尔去喝两杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有店还开着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是回津轻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去见见你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我保持现状就好的 不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 爸爸为什么老是喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸不是喜欢才喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是人太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志津子 父亲 还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太软弱了 是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错不该诞生于世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝太多了吧 在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你知道我是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 醉鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听听我的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前 我让一个女人死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没有生存价值的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.35,0:18:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来不像那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.66,0:18:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 把女人 从悬崖上 推下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.89,0:19:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想活得像个人样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快些来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快推吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你后死太凄凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因为我吐了 所以安眠药没起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只有我活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就编吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则一定是哪里搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会被骗的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的老板娘说你是漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最会编故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间都说我杀了那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世间？世间不就是人的集合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的集合？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那些话 我可不信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你一直待在这里会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.79,0:21:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是喝酒可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.15,0:21:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.03,0:21:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要住这二楼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:22:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么女人都对我这么温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为世间对女人太残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（烟草）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

