Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:55.51,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:23:01.84,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちょっとでも笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:08.03,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつだってこの世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:14.69,ED_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたが必要だから
