Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.99,0:23:19.78,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:23.86,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}We say hello
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:30.95,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}人生在世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:37.54,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}究竟为了追寻什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:42.68,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}睡过头的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:49.34,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也日复一日地清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:23:01.84,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:08.03,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}因为这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.13,0:23:14.69,ED_CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}总是需要你的存在

